        "subject": "LU-12847 docs: add man pages for data_version handling",
        "message": "LU-12847 docs: add man pages for data_version handling\n\nSplit man page for the lfs-data_version(1) command from lfs(1).\nAdd a man page to describe the llapi_get_data_version(3) function.\nAdd long options to the \"lfs data_version\" command while updating\nits man page, since the short option meaningss were not very clear.\n\nAlso add a man page for llapi_hsm_data_version_set(3), since it is\nrelated and was missing its own man page.\n\nAdd a proper example for llapi_fsync(3), instead of referencing lfs.c,\nsince it is implemented via llapi_get_data_version() internally.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nFixes: 80a961261a (\"LU-17863 hsm: add ioctl to set data version in HSM xattr\")\nFixes: 61e3e2d698 (\"LU-930 doc: update data_version command in lfs man page\")\nFixes: de7fe0875b (\"LU-827 lov: Implement a per file data_version.\")\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: I1a34085396b5ab2e229c2244494d722f93aa481d\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/63150\nReviewed-by: Frederick Dilger <fdilger@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Emoly Liu <emoly@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
